overview.longBusinessSummary: Teekay Tankers Ltd. provides marine transportation services to oil industries in Bermuda and internationally. The company offers voyage and time charter services; offshore ship-to-ship transfer of commodities primarily crude oil and refined oil products; and tanker commercial and technical management services. It is also involved in the vessels management, procurement, and equipment rental businesses. The company was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Hamilton, Bermuda.
